        <div class="frame frame-desktop edge-left dark sr-left">
          <img src="./images/work/gray-langur/section7-screen.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain">
        </div> 
      </div>
      <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md column half-md">
        <div class="inner-block-content container">
          <h2 class="case-block-heading">Customs meets&nbsp;<br />custom</h2>
          <p class="case-block-text">
            Gone is a never-ending passport and customs form. Instead, we focus on what matters, in an order that makes sense to users, not diplomats.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block red">
      <img src="./images/work/gray-langur/banner3.jpg" alt="" class="block-image">
    </section>

    <section class="block row black">
      <div class="inner-block absolute-center-md padded column half-md">
        <div class="inner-block-content container">
          <h2 class="case-block-heading">A pocket guide</h2>
          <p class="case-block-text">
            Users aren&rsquo;t dragging their desktops to the airport. Our mobile UI shows everything from stops to who&rsquo;s rooming with who.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="inner-block column half-md hide-overflow gray">
        <img src="./images/work/gray-langur/section8-screen.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image full-height">
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="block red">
      <img src="./images/work/gray-langur/banner4.jpg" alt="" class="block-image">
    </section>

    <section class="block padded-top gray">
      <div class="container row">
        <div class="inner-block column half-md two-third-lg">
          <div class="frame frame-desktop dark sr-bottom">
            <img src="./images/work/gray-langur/section9-screen.jpg" alt="" class="inner-block-image contain">
          </div> 
        </div>
        <div class="inner-block padded-bottom column half-md one-third-lg">
          <div class="inner-block-content gutter-left">
            <h2 class="case-block-heading">Destination:&nbsp;<br />headquarters</h2>
            <p class="case-block-text">
              Gray Langur agents can tailor every last part of each trip through a powerful backend, that lets them dynamically respond to conditions on the ground.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="case-referral centered row">
      <div class="inner-block padded column off-white">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="case-referral-quote-icon"></div>
          <p class="case-referral-text centered">&ldquo;I have, admittedly, fallen in love with Brave and the Brave process over the course of this partnership. The team&rsquo;s passion can easily be seen through their work and the amount of attention they give to each and every detail. It&rsquo;s not often you come across a team that is so perfectly synced and organized and I only hope Gray Langur can emulate that level of awesomeness.&rdquo;</p>
          <p class="case-referral-author">Gabriel Cubbage, <em>CEO, Gray Langur</em></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-block padded">
      <a href="./work/upfront" class="cta-button cta-button-left" title="Previous Case">Previous Case</a>
      <div class="cta-content container">
